  <h1>Assignment 1 - A Simple Drum beat</h1>
  <p>For this assignment, you will email me your completed project file.</p>
  <ol>
    <h2>Assignment instructions</h2>
    <li>Start a new project, and change the pattern length to 32 lines.</li>
    <li>Select a Kick, Snare (or Clap) and Closed Hi-Hat and create a simple drum beat. Try to make the beat effective by keeping the snare steady on beats 2 & 4</li>
    <li>Duplicate your drum pattern and experiment with creating a variation by adding or removing Drum hits.</li>
    <li>In addition to your first pattern, your completed project should have at least 3 Variations</li>
  </ol>
